    A FilterSet for the Category model.

    This filter allows querying Categories based on various criteria.

    Fields:
    - title: Filter by category title (case-insensitive, partial match)
    - products_count: Filter for the exact number of products of a category
    - products_count_range: Range filter for the number of products of a category

    Examples:
